{"tid":1672415,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"建立旅遊資訊推廣到海外有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-10-24T05:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T06:22:48.000Z","uid":172233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee2c34e4498406ed30883c59210a55a19cb19f8","tid":1672415,"uid":172233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的，飲食業有組群提出支持黃店計劃，都好成功幫助好多黃店商戶<br />\n<br />\n如果把這計劃推廣到海外（政府支持旅遊業我哋要幫手）整個香港良心店指南，列明邊啲應該去，邊的唔好去，直情有問題的企業（例：國太）都整埋，一方便讓他們專心祖國發展，另一方面真正地支持香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 我絕對識講唔識整，但有冇得諗，同正唔正先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a102f408bd50075ad2d62e36bd23f1f8b9255442","tid":1672415,"uid":183834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mRT5qBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmRT5qBj.jpg&h=c9cb36e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hQfNPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hQfNPE.jpg&h=882df6eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a876868dcf3347095b9d83acceb15103e195ca99","tid":1672415,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:00:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoa6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=d1a3317c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoa6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=454bcd04\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoa6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=7446e20d\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoa6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=1e58816b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"7d640d7212286beacbe066606cfadedd79c7d3d5","tid":1672415,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"好主意<br />\n一黎幫到黃店<br />\n二黎多數黃店先有真正地道特色<br />\n<br />\n最好有埋推介酒店或旅館"},{"pid":"848d772f3612337061f2fcd0d3eb6ea256328b64","tid":1672415,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"TripAdvisor戰線？"},{"pid":"c74c536e1ecc902863c335f8460f1b60308f7add","tid":1672415,"uid":172233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"848d772f3612337061f2fcd0d3eb6ea256328b64","tid":1672415,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"TripAdvisor戰線？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"Good woo,但始終企業平台，阿爺一定嘈，到時又要下架；所以要有幾手準備，同要英文爸絲幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9716267e4a224e26d9be5a09945f25b442d3c5e3","tid":1672415,"uid":99397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:13:55.000Z","msg":"支持，要幫手預埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b21691633fbfc734d38084f7a56f16f9d9143dc","tid":1672415,"uid":278435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"如果你聯絡到<br />\n係有得做<br />\n<br />\n最初youtube個西多士都係拍香港野食<br />\n但係難做，好店本來就好生意唔洗你拍<br />\n小店你拍又比人話收錢買like<br />\n你要小心間店係唔係真係好食同你要正確<br />\n如果間野好難食你叫左人去會比人X 你<br />\n香港d鋪係唔鐘意你去拍攝阻住佢"}]}